## Decision Trees

### Choosing Which Primitive

```
Need to interact with UI?
│
├─ Just checking state? → agent.verify()
│
├─ Extracting data? → agent.extract()
│
├─ Know exact coordinates?
│  ├─ Yes → computer.mouse.click_at() or computer.hotkey()/computer.press()
│  └─ No → agent.execute()
│
└─ Complex multi-step?
   └─ agent.execute() with clear description
```

### Choosing Timeout Values

```
Operation Type          | Timeout
-----------------------|----------
Button visibility      | 5s
Page load             | 30s
Form submission       | 20s
File download         | 60-120s
Long async operation  | 180s+
```

### Choosing Max Iterations

```
Task Complexity        | Max Iterations
----------------------|----------------
Simple click          | 3-5
Form filling          | 10-15
Complex sequence      | 20-30
Loops/iteration       | 40-60
```

